    {
      "chinese": "「Paradiway」的吟唱方式，由領導者領唱，年齡階級的群體和聲回應，猶如領導和部落的群體相互對話一樣。這種「miparadiw」的吟唱方式有三個重要的意義。首先，是作為呼喚已故的長輩表示感恩之歌。每當部落的豐年祭的開幕儀式，必須由頭目或由大統領帶領吟詩向已故的長輩宣示，向祂們稟告部落的活動，祈願祂們賜福部落族人生活富裕、五穀豐收及青年人狩獵捕魚大有所獲。",
      "ab": "U “Paradiway” hananay a radiwan, u miparadiway ku mikeriday, u selal tu ku micararadaway a pacauv, matiya tu u mikeriday atu masasuwalay nu alumanay. Tulu ku tapang a paini. Saayaway, miangang a paradiw, a miaray tu malasawaday tu nu matuasay. \r\n[===]\r\nYu malingatu a malalikid, caay kanca kaw tumuk anusa u kaka nu mamikeriday a paluku pavana’ tu malasawaday tu nu matuasay, pavana’ tu demak nu niyaru’, milunguc tu sakakapah nu niyaru’, a adihayen ku sadak tu nikaumahan, sarahiden ku nikaalaan i piadupan atu pivutinagan.",
      "order": "2",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2022/11/23/75859e2aadee7dd0e8a9521a63d061f2.wav",
